{
  "stem": "4345.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the toilet was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every day, we used to go through outside to the backyard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a communal toilet, sort of.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And babies cried because the mothers were-- didn't have enough food for them, little babies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I-- this one mother was sitting outside feeding her baby on the step, and this-- this SS man goes by.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she says, I am [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said to her, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm giving my child to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went over to close to her-- close to her, takes out a little bayonet, one of those short ones, and he cuts off the breast.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the baby is left with the breast in the mouth and the mother died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These are the-- these are the horrific stories that the Nazis did to our people, to our mothers, to our babies.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then, they had the trained dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is a-- a later story, as I'm going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I came running home to Mommy and I told her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she says, Mila, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't go out and don't look, please.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Please just stay-- be still and don't let anybody see you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I tried very much to hold-- to-- to compose myself and not to do this, but I was young and I did not care.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was very-- I was inquisitive and sometimes to my disadvantage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went back-- I went back into the house and, you know, an epidemic broke out and the children started, from hunger and from-- from illness, from dirt, no diapers, no nothing, people got sick.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they had a good reason to exterminate people because they're spreading an epidemic.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
